        <item>
            <title>Version 3.16.7</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 19 May 2026 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>57</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.16.7</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Built-in player renamed "Setlist (Built-In Player)" — appears first in the player list and is now the default for fresh installs, with a "Recommended" badge in Settings › Player</li>
                    <li>Cortina denylist editor redesigned as a cleaner three-column layout (Genre | Display label | Controls)</li>
                    <li>Setlist state (paused, queued, played) now persists to disk immediately</li>
                    <li>Context menu now shows only relevant options depending on track state</li>
                    <li>Removed unused "Last Tanda Label" colour setting from Appearance › Colours</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
