            <sparkle:version>55</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.16.5</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Add tracks by pressing ⌘V — copy audio files in Finder, Music.app, or Swinsian with ⌘C, then press ⌘V while the Setlist panel is focused to append them instantly</li>
