        <item>
            <title>Version 3.16.3</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 18 May 2026 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>53</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>3.16.3</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Add customisable genre tag colours to the Setlist player. Assign a colour to any genre keyword — keywords match case-insensitively and partially (e.g. "tango" matches "Argentine Tango"). Colours apply only to upcoming unplayed tracks; playing, paused, and already-played tracks keep their standard colours.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
